Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飛跨命運的山崖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:06.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿越縛束的鐐枷  一直伴在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:23.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}隻身一人面對  在那場戰鬥中了知的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:28.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也許一切都無法做出變化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:29.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但我依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:35.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}會帶著那身殘破的兵甲  去把你救下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:45.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在遙遠記憶的盡頭  在時間終結之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:47.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Far  away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:48.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Find  the  way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:49.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Fly  Fafnir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}超越才能向上攀爬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:57.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用你的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去看清所有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飛跨命運的山崖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:08.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿越縛束的鐐枷  一直伴在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向遠方射出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}FLYING  FAFNIR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ただ一つの愛を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:21.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}果てない空を裂いた光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:36.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}信じることはとても難しいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:49.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君が笑えば胸が痛み出すのは何故でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:53.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}線が走り　呼吸響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:59.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この夜空を越えて行けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:04.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幾度と無く傷つくのに馴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心に咲く花が枯れ果てても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何度でも君を求める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:20.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}踊れ　世界が向かうままに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:25.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}嘘のない言葉でさあ撃ち抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:30.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ただ一つの愛を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:36.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}果てない空を裂いた光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}擁抱唯一僅有的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:21.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}讓光把無邊的天空切割開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:36.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}信任是如此的艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:49.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}看到你的笑容  為何心中隱約作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}劃過的線條  奔跑時的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:59.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}超越了夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:04.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即便早已習慣了受傷流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}綻放在心中的花朵盡數枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對你無數次的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:20.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歡跳在這被束縛的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:25.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}用真實的話語  去擊穿吧
